gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nets 102, Wizards 94
gameRecap.excerpt: After closing the game on a 14-2 run, the Nets defeated the Wizards, 102-94. Mikal Bridges led all scorers with 27 points and a career-high 13 rebounds for the Nets, while Bilal Coulibaly tallied a career-high 20 points for the Wizards in the losing effort. The Nets improve to 5-5 on the season, while the Wizards fall to 2-7.
